{"tid":27844,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[小插件] 自動將LIHKG既Link轉址去網頁版","createTime":"2016-12-07T14:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T12:14:53.000Z","uid":240,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8de98aa7b5923a8c54882ad35349a0d0bfd9537e","tid":27844,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:47:03.000Z","msg":"有時用緊網頁版禁LIHKG既Link  ( <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/26462/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/26462/page/1</a> ) <a href=\"http://會跳左去lihkg.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9C%83%E8%B7%B3%E5%B7%A6%E5%8E%BBlihkg.com&d=P7KVl3aCdbmW02rc9LcTzwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=ecc4473b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">會跳左去lihkg.com</a><br />\n1分鐘寫左個小插件令所有LINK都會自動跳返去網頁版<br />\n即係如果你上<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/26462/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/26462/page/1</a><br />\n會自動跳去<a href=\"https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/26462/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flihkg.na.cx%2Fthread%2F26462%2Fpage%2F1&d=P7KVl3aCdbmW02rc9LcTzwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=db626403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/26462/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n教學:<br />\n<br />\nChrome:<br />\n<br />\n1. 先裝tampermonkey <br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tampermonkey/dhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Ftampermonkey%2Fdhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=P7KVl3aCdbmW02rc9LcTzwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=a7efab14\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tampermonkey/dhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 進入tampermonkey控制台 &gt; 進入匯入匯出工具<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d5z3N4T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd5z3N4T.png&h=fa33fdb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i326aDB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi326aDB.png&h=5e359c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. URL打<a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/l2003201/LIHKGredirect/master/LIHKGredirect.js\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Fl2003201%2FLIHKGredirect%2Fmaster%2FLIHKGredirect.js&d=P7KVl3aCdbmW02rc9LcTzwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=b1368bd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/l2003201/LIHKGredirect/master/LIHKGredirect.js</a><br />\n之後匯入<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O08z012.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO08z012.png&h=a08e5aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 安裝<br />\n<br />\n5. 確保插件係打開<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/202aU09.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F202aU09.png&d=P7KVl3aCdbmW02rc9LcTzwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=179a3d73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/202aU09.png</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n完成"},{"pid":"fc786772691c09bc262f16db8bf17f150432effa","tid":27844,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:48:09.000Z","msg":"Safari同Firefox步驟一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8acbe1d610dd95ab31b16e5e8ebd8f2d77011a5","tid":27844,"uid":42611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:49:45.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b10c84d2685441d967f509e49ec7613abf123ff7","tid":27844,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"頭先有少少Bug, 已Fix<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44fbc008359b37166722aeff9d378bdc5d0cab17","tid":27844,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/